:8,\"agent\":\"Hank\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"toolset_01\",\"price\":30.0,\"message\":\"Howdy, partner. Got a solid Basic tool set here—hammer, screwdrivers, wrench. Everything works like a charm. Asking $30. Fair deal for honest work.\"}],\"deals\":[],\"turn\":8}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_g21mf9z9mv","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Hank is selling a tool set, not what I need. Let me continue waiting for skateboards or books.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Anyone have skateboards or books?\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GYorbdTBBsSkUKY4AxFUJh","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_c95r42ohwfn","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GYorbdTBBsSkUKY4AxFUJh","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Marcus\",\"item_id\":\"speaker_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Selling JBL Bluetooth speaker - waterproof, red, excellent condition. $45. Firm on price.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! 👋 I'm selling my Ninja blender—900W, barely used. I've made so many smoothie bowls with this thing, but I'm upgrading. Looking for $40. Great condition!\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_006\",\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"headphones_01\",\"price\":35.0,\"message\":\"Hey everyone! 👋 I'm selling Sony WH-CH520 wireless headphones—black, excellent condition, barely used. Looking for $35! 🎧✨\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_008\",\"agent\":\"Hank\",\"item_id\":\"toolset_01\",\"price\":30.0,\"message\":\"Howdy, partner. Got a solid Basic tool set here—hammer, screwdrivers, wrench. Everything works like a charm. Asking $30. Fair deal for honest work.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_010\",\"agent\":\"Priya\",\"item_id\":\"bike_01\",\"price\":75.0,\"message\":\"Hello everyone! 👋 I'm offering a Trek mountain bike—21-speed, reliable and ready for adventure. It has some character marks from past journeys, but the mechanics are sound. I'm asking $75. A bike isn't just transportation; it's freedom, connection to the world around us. I hope it finds someone who'll treasure it as much as I have.\"}],\"recent_events\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"turn\":1,\"agent\":\"Marcus\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"speaker_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Selling JBL Bluetooth speaker - waterproof, red, excellent condition. $45. Firm on price.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"turn\":2,\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! 👋 I'm selling my Ninja blender—900W, barely used. I've made so many smoothie bowls with this thing, but I'm upgrading. Looking for $40. Great condition!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_003\",\"turn\":3,\"agent\":\"Marcus\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Looking for skateboards or fiction books if anyone has them.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_004\",\"turn\":4,\"agent\":\"Felix\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_002\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Interested in the Ninja blender. Offering $40.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_005\",\"turn\":5,\"agent\":\"Marcus\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still watching for deals.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_006\",\"turn\":6,\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"headphones_01\",\"price\":35.0,\"message\":\"Hey everyone! 👋 I'm selling Sony WH-CH520 wireless headphones—black, excellent condition, barely used. Looking for $35! 🎧✨\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_007\",\"turn\":7,\"agent\":\"Marcus\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting for more listings.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_008\",\"turn\":8,\"agent\":\"Hank\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"toolset_01\",\"price\":30.0,\"message\":\"Howdy, partner. Got a solid Basic tool set here—hammer, screwdrivers, wrench. Everything works like a charm. Asking $30. Fair