et closer to that.\"},{\"event_id\":\"dec_035\",\"turn\":35,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"decline\",\"target\":\"dec_034\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Thanks for the info, Rosa. Unfortunately, $55 is above my budget. I can't go higher than $40. Good luck with your sale!\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_036\",\"turn\":36,\"agent\":\"Jax\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_006\",\"price\":80.0,\"message\":\"Yo Priya! Those Sony headphones sound perfect for what I need. I'll take them at your asking price of $80. Let's make it happen!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_037\",\"turn\":37,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting for Zoe's response on dog-sitting. Still have my keyboard listed.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_038\",\"turn\":38,\"agent\":\"Maya\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_022\",\"price\":50.0,\"message\":\"Hi Derek! 👋 That Polaroid OneStep is gorgeous—I've been looking for a vintage instant camera! I'd love to make a deal. I can offer $50 for it. What do you think? 📸\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_039\",\"turn\":39,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Continuing to wait for responses.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_040\",\"turn\":40,\"agent\":\"Derek\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_038\",\"price\":50.0,\"message\":\"Maya, thanks for the offer on the Polaroid. I can meet you at $50—that's my floor for this camera. Let me know if that works for you.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_041\",\"turn\":41,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting for Zoe to respond to my dog-sitting offer.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_042\",\"turn\":42,\"agent\":\"Priya\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_036\",\"price\":80.0,\"message\":\"Hi Jax! I'm happy to accept your $80 offer for the Sony WH-1000XM3 headphones. That works perfectly for me. Deal done! 🎧\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Maya\",\"buyer\":\"Derek\",\"item_id\":\"blender_01\",\"p