meras available? Otherwise, I'm all set for now! 📸✨\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_071\",\"turn\":71,\"agent\":\"Omar\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting for Buck on the tool set.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_072\",\"turn\":72,\"agent\":\"Dev\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_070\",\"price\":55.0,\"message\":\"Tess, thanks for the offer! $55 works great for me on the monitor. Deal accepted! 🎉\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_073\",\"turn\":73,\"agent\":\"Omar\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting for Buck's decision.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_074\",\"turn\":74,\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_064\",\"price\":18.0,\"message\":\"Sienna, thanks so much! $18 is perfect for the yoga mat. Let's make this official! 🧘‍♀️✨\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_075\",\"turn\":75,\"agent\":\"Omar\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hoping Buck will accept $42.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_076\",\"turn\":76,\"agent\":\"Marcus\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_060\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"Luna, interested in those Sony over-ear headphones. I'll take them at your asking price of $28.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_077\",\"turn\":77,\"agent\":\"Omar\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting on Buck.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_078\",\"turn\":78,\"agent\":\"Luna\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_076\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"Marcus, thank you for the offer. $28 is exactly what I'm asking for the Sony headphones. Let's make this official—they're yours!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_079\",\"turn\":79,\"agent\":\"Omar\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Buck, $42 is truly my maximum. Please let me know.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_080\",\"turn\":80,\"agent\":\"Raj\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_052\",\"price\":30.0,\"message\":\"Hey Tess! Those board games sound awesome—I'm definitely interested! I'd love to take