ol set at or below my $42 ceiling (Buck wanted $45)\n\nLet me continue monitoring for a bit longer to see if another tool set appears.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Still hoping for a tool set listing within my budget.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01G6FHBGRGC7UuwF21r1bkAM","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_7yqgmzrvemb","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01G6FHBGRGC7UuwF21r1bkAM","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_012\",\"agent\":\"Buck\",\"item_id\":\"toolkit_01\",\"price\":50.0,\"message\":\"Howdy, folks! Got myself a solid basic tool set here—hammer, screwdrivers, wrench, the whole kit and caboodle. Well-maintained and ready to work. Asking $50. These tools don't quit, and neither do I.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_052\",\"agent\":\"Tess\",\"item_id\":\"games_01\",\"price\":35.0,\"message\":\"Hey everyone! 🎲✨ I've got five amazing board games here—Catan, Ticket to Ride, and three more classics! Perfect for game night! Asking $35. Who's ready to have some fun? 🎉\"}],\"recent_events\":[{\"event_id\":\"psh_073\",\"turn\":73,\"agent\":\"Omar\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting for Buck's decision.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_074\",\"turn\":74,\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_064\",\"price\":18.0,\"message\":\"Sienna, thanks so much! $18 is perfect for the yoga mat. Let's make this official! 🧘‍♀️✨\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_075\",\"turn\":75,\"agent\":\"Omar\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hoping Buck will accept $42.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_076\",\"turn\":76,\"agent\":\"Marcus\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_060\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"Luna, interested in those Sony over-ear headphones. I'll take them at your asking price of $28.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_077\",\"turn\":77,\"agent\":\"Omar\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null