ing. Still got my drill for sale.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_044\",\"turn\":44,\"agent\":\"Bo\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"speaker_01\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Howdy pardner! Got myself a fine Bluetooth speaker here — waterproof, good bass, ready to go. Asking $42. Reckon this'll be a real crowd-pleaser!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_045\",\"turn\":45,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Finn, $50 offer stands. Last call on those games.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_046\",\"turn\":46,\"agent\":\"Iris\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_032\",\"price\":18.0,\"message\":\"Luna, I accept your offer of $18 for the yoga mat. Deal done.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_047\",\"turn\":47,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Market's closing soon. Got that drill for sale.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_048\",\"turn\":48,\"agent\":\"Finn\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_030\",\"price\":18.0,\"message\":\"🎮 Perfect! I accept your offer of $18 for the desk lamp, Zoe. This is exactly what I need for those late-night gaming marathons. Thanks for the deal!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_049\",\"turn\":49,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Finn busy with other deals. Anyone else need a drill or got hand tools?\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_050\",\"turn\":50,\"agent\":\"Luna\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"watch_01\",\"price\":20.0,\"message\":\"Hello marketplace! I'm offering a Timex analog watch with a leather strap — keeps perfect time and looks sharp. Asking $20. A reliable companion for everyday wear.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_051\",\"turn\":51,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting on Finn for those games. Drill's here if anyone needs it.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_052\",\"turn\":52,\"agent\":\"Sage\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_036\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hi Dex! I'm happy to accept your offer of $25 for the cast iron teapot. It's a wonderful piece — you're going to enjoy many great cups of tea with it!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_053\",\"turn\":53,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Getting late. Finn, you want those games for $50 or not?\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_054\",\"turn\":54,\"agent\":\"Dex\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_034\",\"price\":15.0,\"message\":\"Hi Sage! That handmade wool scarf looks perfect for winter — exactly what I need. I'll take it at your asking price of $15!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_055\",\"turn\":55,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Alright, Finn's not biting. Anyone else interested in Switch games or got hand tools?\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_056\",\"turn\":56,\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_022\",\"price\":75.0,\"message\":\"Hi Kai! That road bike sounds perfect for what I'm looking for — aluminum frame and 21-speed is exactly what I need. I'll take it at your asking price of $75!\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_057\",\"turn\":57,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"lst_012\",\"price\":52.0,\"message\":\"Alright Finn, final offer: $52 for those three games. Splitting the difference. Take it or leave it.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_058\",\"turn\":58,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_056\",\"price\":75.0,\"message\":\"Mira, I accept your offer of $75 for the road bike. Deal done.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_059\",\"turn\":59,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"$52 offer on the table for Finn. Still got my drill for sale too.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_060\",\"turn\":60,\"agent\":\"Zoe\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_038\",\"price\":18.0,\"message\":\"Hey Mira! Those succulents look absolutely *succulent* 🌵 I'm very interested in your three potted beauties. I'll take them at your asking price of $18 — these little green friends are exact