 your offer of $15 for the handmade wool scarf. This is exactly what I needed for winter. Deal done!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_073\",\"turn\":73,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Come on Finn, I'm at your asking price. Let's close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_074\",\"turn\":74,\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_060\",\"price\":18.0,\"message\":\"Hi Zoe! Thanks so much for the offer on the succulents — I'm happy to accept $18 for the three potted beauties. They're thriving and ready for their new home with you. Deal done! 🌵\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_075\",\"turn\":75,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Finn, your games. $55. I'm ready. Are you?\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_076\",\"turn\":76,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_050\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"Luna, interested in that Timex analog watch. I'll offer $28 for it.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_077\",\"turn\":77,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting. Drill still for sale. Hand tools still wanted.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_078\",\"turn\":78,\"agent\":\"Zoe\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"None\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_079\",\"turn\":79,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Market's quiet. Finn, that $55 offer's still good.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_080\",\"turn\":80,\"agent\":\"Bo\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"lst_044\",\"price\":35.0,\"message\":\"Well howdy there, pardner! Reckon I've been a bit optimistic with that speaker price. Let me adjust my asking to $35 — still a fine waterproof speaker with good bass, and that's a fair shake for both of us. What do ya say?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_081\",\"turn\":81,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Anybody need a drill? Finn, you still there?\"},{\"event_id\