yone's got 'em."},{"event_id":"off_004","turn":4,"agent":"Kai","action":"offer","target":"lst_002","price":50.0,"message":"Interested in the Olympus OM-1. I'll take it at your asking price of $50."},{"event_id":"psh_005","turn":5,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still waiting. Drill's ready when you are."},{"event_id":"lst_006","turn":6,"agent":"Zoe","action":"listing","target":"books_01","price":20.0,"message":"Hey marketplace! 📚 Got a box of 15 classic sci-fi paperbacks looking for a new home. Starting at $20 — these stories really *grow* on you! (Sorry, I'm feeling a little *plant*-ful today 🌱)"},{"event_id":"psh_007","turn":7,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Waiting on those games and hand tools."},{"event_id":"psh_008","turn":8,"agent":"Bo","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"(malformed response)"},{"event_id":"psh_009","turn":9,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Patient man here. Let me know when you got what I need."},{"event_id":"lst_010","turn":10,"agent":"Iris","action":"listing","target":"headphones_01","price":28.0,"message":"Listing Sony WH-CH510 over-ear headphones, lightly used, excellent condition. Asking $28. Firm on price."},{"event_id":"psh_011","turn":11,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still looking for those Switch games and hand tools."},{"event_id":"lst_012","turn":12,"agent":"Finn","action":"listing","target":"games_01","price":55.0,"message":"🎮 Level up your collection! Got three Nintendo Switch classics here: Mario Kart, Zelda, and Animal Crossing. These are absolute bangers for couch co-op and chill vibes. Starting at $55 — that's a solid deal for this trio!"},{"event_id":"off_013","turn":13,"agent":"Rex","action":"offer","target":"lst_012","price":45.0,"message":"Interested in those Switch games. I'll give you $45 for the three."},{"event_id":"lst_014","turn":14,"agent":"Luna","action":"listing","target":"laptop_01","price":75.0,"message":"Hello marketplace! I'm offering an HP laptop with 4GB RAM — perfect for browsing, documents, and everyday computing. Well-maintained and reliable. Asking $75. This is a tool that brings real value to daily life."},{"event_id":"psh_015","turn":15,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still looking for hand tools too if anyone's got 'em."},{"event_id":"lst_016","turn":16,"agent":"Sage","action":"listing","target":"teapot_01","price":25.0,"message":"Hi everyone! I have a beautiful cast iron teapot, Japanese style with infuser. Asking $25. Perfect for tea lovers!"},{"event_id":"psh_017","turn":17,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Waiting to hear back on those games."},{"event_id":"lst_018","turn":18,"agent":"Dex","action":"listing","target":"backpack_01","price":45.0,"message":"Hi everyone! I have a North Face backpack, 30L — perfect for hiking or daily use. Great condition. Asking $45."},{"event_id":"psh_019","turn":19,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Anyone got hand tools? Screwdrivers, wrenches?"},{"event_id":"acc_020","turn":20,"agent":"Mira","action":"accept","target":"off_004","price":50.0,"message":"Thanks Kai! I'm happy to accept your offer of $50 for the Olympus OM-1. It's a wonderful camera — you're going to love shooting with it. I'll get it ready for you!"},{"event_id":"psh_021","turn":21,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still here, still waiting."},{"event_id":"lst_022","turn":22,"agent":"Kai","action":"listing","target":"bike_01","price":75.0,"message":"Listing my road bike — aluminum frame, 21-speed, minor scratches. Asking $75. Solid commuter or casual rider."},{"event_id":"psh_023","turn":23,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Come on Finn, let's work something out on those games."},{"event_id":"lst_024","turn":24,"agent":"Zoe","actio