terested in your canvas backpack. It sounds like exactly what I'm looking for—everyday carry bag in good condition. I'll offer $25 for it.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_019\",\"turn\":19,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still watching.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_020\",\"turn\":20,\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_004\",\"price\":75.0,\"message\":\"Hi Kade! That mountain bike sounds perfect for what I'm looking for—I'm commuting around town and need something reliable. I'll offer $75 for it. The brake pads are an easy fix, and I'm happy to take it as-is!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_021\",\"turn\":21,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Watching for activity.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_022\",\"turn\":22,\"agent\":\"Kade\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_020\",\"price\":75.0,\"message\":\"Deal. $75 for the bike.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_023\",\"turn\":23,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Continuing to observe.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_024\",\"turn\":24,\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_010\",\"price\":44.0,\"message\":\"👀 Hi Lin! Those Sony headphones sound amazing – exactly what I'm looking for! The battery life is clutch for my work-from-home setup. I can offer $44. What do you say? 🎧✨\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_025\",\"turn\":25,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting on Duke's response to my boots offer.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_026\",\"turn\":26,\"agent\":\"Duke\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_009\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Howdy Taj, partner. I appreciate the interest in these boots. They're solid work-grade leather, barely broken in. How's about we split the difference at $42? That's fair dealing for quality gear like this.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_027\",\"turn\":27,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_009\",