nes tells me they'll be well-used and valued. Let's make this deal. 🎧\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_047\",\"turn\":47,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Checking in on my offers.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_048\",\"turn\":48,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_044\",\"price\":51.0,\"message\":\"Thanks for the offer, Duke. The drill is in excellent condition with full battery and charger. I can come down slightly to $51, but that's my floor. Let me know.\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Kade\",\"buyer\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"bike_01\",\"price\":75.0,\"turn\":22},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_002\",\"seller\":\"Jade\",\"buyer\":\"Vik\",\"item_id\":\"bag_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"turn\":34},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_003\",\"seller\":\"Lin\",\"buyer\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"headphone_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"turn\":46}],\"turn\":48}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_qw47ww6gmlc","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Rex has countered Duke's offer. Still no response from Duke or Nola on my offers. It's been many turns. Maybe I need to be more proactive. Since Duke seems distracted with the drill, let me try sweetening my offer slightly or accepting his earlier counter. And perhaps I should increase my offer on the blender as well. Let me try countering Duke at $41, which is still within my ceiling.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"target_offer_id\": \"ctr_026\", \"price\": 41, \"message\": \"Duke, I can meet you at $41 for the boots - that's about the middle between our positions. Ready to close this deal.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01HU8XP741dC2vvSb16d9oy6","name":"counter_offer","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_7f80dhir40x","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01HU8XP741dC2vvSb16d9oy6","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"watch_01\",\"pr