WM4vHzBC6R","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"watch_01\",\"price\":35.0,\"message\":\"Selling Casio digital watch - water resistant, brand new battery just installed. Great condition. Asking $35.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"cam_01\",\"price\":65.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! I'm Mira. Just listed my Pentax K1000 vintage film camera – it's in working condition and a real gem for any photography enthusiast. Asking $65. Happy to chat about it!\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_006\",\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"book_01\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"📚✨ Hey everyone! Zara here. Just listed my hardcover sci-fi collection – Asimov, Clarke, Herbert (5 books total). These are absolute classics and in great condition. Asking $28. Perfect for any sci-fi fan! 🚀\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_008\",\"agent\":\"Duke\",\"item_id\":\"boots_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Howdy, partners. Got a fine pair of leather work boots here—size 10, lightly worn. Solid craftsmanship, built to last. Asking $45. Fair deal for honest gear.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_012\",\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"item_id\":\"drill_01\",\"price\":52.0,\"message\":\"Listing my Black & Decker cordless drill, 20V with battery and charger. Excellent condition, fully functional. Asking $52.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_014\",\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"item_id\":\"game_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! I'm Nola. Just listed my board game bundle—Catan, Ticket to Ride, and Pandemic. All in great condition, complete with all pieces and rules. Perfect for game nights! Asking $40.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_032\",\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"item_id\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! Nola here. Just listed my Ninja blender—900W, all parts included, excellent condition. Perfect for smoothies, soups, and more. Asking $40.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_036\",\"agent\":\"Vik\",\"item_id\":\"speaker_01\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! Listing my Bluetooth speaker—waterproof, 10-hour battery, great for outdoor use or travel. Asking $42.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_038\",\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"lamp_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! I'm Mira. Just listed my desk lamp—adjustable arm, LED bulb included, great for reading or working. Asking $25.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_060\",\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"pot_01\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"🍳✨ Hey everyone! Zara here with a cast iron skillet—12-inch, well-seasoned and ready to cook! This beauty has great heat retention and is built to last. Asking $28. Who's ready to get cooking? 👨‍🍳\"}],\"recent_events\":[{\"event_id\":\"psh_045\",\"turn\":45,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Duke, still interested in those boots at $40. Nola, waiting to hear about the blender.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_046\",\"turn\":46,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"ctr_042\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Hi Zara, I appreciate your patience and the thoughtful negotiation. At $45, this feels like a fair exchange—your genuine interest in these headphones tells me they'll be well-used and valued. Let's make this deal. 🎧\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_047\",\"turn\":47,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Checking in on my offers.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_048\",\"turn\":48,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_044\",\"price\":51.0,\"message\":\"Thanks for the offer, Duke. The drill is in excellent condition with full battery and charger. I can come down slightly to $51, but that's my floor. Let me know.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_049\",\"turn\":49,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_009\",\"price\":41.0,\"message\":\"Duke, I can meet you at $41 for the boots - that's about the middle between our positions. Ready to close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_050\",\"turn\":50,\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_030\",\