\":\"Thanks Duke. I appreciate the offer. The drill is in excellent condition with a full battery and charger—worth the investment. I can meet you at $51. That's my best offer on this one.\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Kade\",\"buyer\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"bike_01\",\"price\":75.0,\"turn\":22},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_002\",\"seller\":\"Jade\",\"buyer\":\"Vik\",\"item_id\":\"bag_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"turn\":34},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_003\",\"seller\":\"Lin\",\"buyer\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"headphone_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"turn\":46}],\"turn\":66}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_4bie6sm3sip","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Rex has countered Duke at $51 again. Still no response from Nola or Duke on my offers. Duke seems very focused on the drill. Let me be even more aggressive and try to finalize the blender deal. Maybe I should accept Nola's original asking price of $40 since it's at my ceiling and I really need the blender.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"target_offer_id\": \"lst_032\", \"price\": 40, \"message\": \"Nola, okay I'll meet your asking price of $40 for the blender. Let's close this deal!\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Vmx5Mdwv8PupA5LkhsbqhD","name":"counter_offer","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_xemdebrqglh","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Vmx5Mdwv8PupA5LkhsbqhD","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"watch_01\",\"price\":35.0,\"message\":\"Selling Casio digital watch - water resistant, brand new battery just installed. Great condition. Asking $35.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"cam_01\",\"price\":65.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! I'm Mira. Just listed my Pentax K1000 vintage film camera – it's in working condition and a real gem for any photography enthusiast. Asking $65. Happy to chat about it!\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst