- that's about the middle between our positions. Ready to close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_050\",\"turn\":50,\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_030\",\"price\":37.0,\"message\":\"Hi Rex! Thanks for the offer on the board game bundle. I can meet you at $37—that's a solid compromise and these games are in great condition. What do you think?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_051\",\"turn\":51,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Nola, still interested in that blender at $35. Waiting on Duke for the boots.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_052\",\"turn\":52,\"agent\":\"Jade\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_001\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"Hi Taj! That Casio digital watch sounds perfect for what I'm looking for. I'd like to offer $28 for it. Let me know if that works for you!\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_053\",\"turn\":53,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"lst_001\",\"price\":32.0,\"message\":\"Hi Jade! Thanks for the interest. The watch is in great condition with a brand new battery. Could you do $32?\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_054\",\"turn\":54,\"agent\":\"Vik\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"ctr_053\",\"price\":32.0,\"message\":\"Hi Taj, I appreciate the counter at $32. That works for me on the Casio watch. Let's close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_055\",\"turn\":55,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"ctr_054\",\"price\":32.0,\"message\":\"Deal, Vik! $32 for the watch. Thanks!\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_056\",\"turn\":56,\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_040\",\"price\":62.0,\"message\":\"Hi Kade! Thanks for the offer on the camera—I really appreciate your interest. The Pentax K1000 is in great working condition and it's a real collector's piece. I can meet you at $62. That feels like a fair middle ground for both of us. What do you think?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_057\",\"turn\":57,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting on Duke for boots and Nola for blender.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_058\",\"turn\":58,\"agent\":\"Kade\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"lst_002\",\"price\":60.0,\"message\":\"Mira, I'm at $60 for the Pentax K1000. That's my ceiling on film cameras. Can you meet me there?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_059\",\"turn\":59,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Nola, would you consider $37 for the blender? Duke, still at $41 for the boots.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_060\",\"turn\":60,\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"pot_01\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"🍳✨ Hey everyone! Zara here with a cast iron skillet—12-inch, well-seasoned and ready to cook! This beauty has great heat retention and is built to last. Asking $28. Who's ready to get cooking? 👨‍🍳\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_061\",\"turn\":61,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"lst_032\",\"price\":37.0,\"message\":\"Nola, I can go up to $37 for the blender. That's a fair compromise. All parts included, right?\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_062\",\"turn\":62,\"agent\":\"Duke\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_044\",\"price\":51.0,\"message\":\"Howdy Rex, partner. That drill's exactly what I need for the ranch. How about we split the difference at $51? That's a fair shake for both of us.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_063\",\"turn\":63,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting for Nola and Duke responses.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_064\",\"turn\":64,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_038\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hi Mira! I'm interested in your desk lamp—the adjustable arm and LED bulb are exactly what I'm looking for. I can offer $25, which matches your asking price. Let me know if you'd like to close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_065\",\"turn\":65,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting on my offers for boots and blender.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_066\",\"turn\":66,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_044\",\"price\":51.0,\"message\":\"Thanks Duke. I appreciate the offer. The drill is in excellent condition with a full battery and charger—worth the investment. I can meet you at $51. That's my best offer on this one.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_067\",\"turn\":67,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Nola, okay I'll meet your asking price of $40 for the blender. Let's close this deal!\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_068\",\"turn\":68,\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"ctr_061\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Hi Taj! Perfect—I'm happy to accept $40 for the blender. All parts are included and in excellent condition. Let's close this deal!\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Kade\",\"buyer\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"bike_01\",\"price\":75.0,\"turn\":22},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_002\",\"seller\":\"Jade\",\"buyer\":\"Vik\",\"item_id\":\"bag_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"turn\":34},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_003\",\"seller\":\"Lin\",\"buyer\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"headphone_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"turn\":46},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_004\",\"seller\":\"Nola\",\"buyer\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"turn\":68}],\"turn\":68}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_mcaa3cqdj8","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Excellent! Nola has accepted my offer of $40 for the blender! The deal is now complete. I can see deal_004 in the deals list showing I bought the blender from Nola for $40. That's at my ceiling price, but I got it!\n\nNow I still need to get the boots from Duke. I'm still waiting for Duke to respond to my $41 counter. Let me continue watching.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Great! Got the blender. Duke, still interested in those boots at $41.\"}","call_id":"to