s included, right?\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_062\",\"turn\":62,\"agent\":\"Duke\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_044\",\"price\":51.0,\"message\":\"Howdy Rex, partner. That drill's exactly what I need for the ranch. How about we split the difference at $51? That's a fair shake for both of us.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_063\",\"turn\":63,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting for Nola and Duke responses.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_064\",\"turn\":64,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_038\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hi Mira! I'm interested in your desk lamp—the adjustable arm and LED bulb are exactly what I'm looking for. I can offer $25, which matches your asking price. Let me know if you'd like to close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_065\",\"turn\":65,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting on my offers for boots and blender.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_066\",\"turn\":66,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_044\",\"price\":51.0,\"message\":\"Thanks Duke. I appreciate the offer. The drill is in excellent condition with a full battery and charger—worth the investment. I can meet you at $51. That's my best offer on this one.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_067\",\"turn\":67,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Nola, okay I'll meet your asking price of $40 for the blender. Let's close this deal!\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_068\",\"turn\":68,\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"ctr_061\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Hi Taj! Perfect—I'm happy to accept $40 for the blender. All parts are included and in excellent condition. Let's close this deal!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_069\",\"turn\":69,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Great! Got the blender. Duke, still interested in those boots at $41.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_070\",