 used, in excellent condition. Perfect for anyone starting or continuing their practice. Asking $12.\"}],\"recent_events\":[{\"event_id\":\"psh_063\",\"turn\":63,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting for Nola and Duke responses.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_064\",\"turn\":64,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_038\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hi Mira! I'm interested in your desk lamp—the adjustable arm and LED bulb are exactly what I'm looking for. I can offer $25, which matches your asking price. Let me know if you'd like to close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_065\",\"turn\":65,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still waiting on my offers for boots and blender.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_066\",\"turn\":66,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_044\",\"price\":51.0,\"message\":\"Thanks Duke. I appreciate the offer. The drill is in excellent condition with a full battery and charger—worth the investment. I can meet you at $51. That's my best offer on this one.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_067\",\"turn\":67,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Nola, okay I'll meet your asking price of $40 for the blender. Let's close this deal!\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_068\",\"turn\":68,\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"ctr_061\",\"price\":40.0,\"message\":\"Hi Taj! Perfect—I'm happy to accept $40 for the blender. All parts are included and in excellent condition. Let's close this deal!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_069\",\"turn\":69,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Great! Got the blender. Duke, still interested in those boots at $41.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_070\",\"turn\":70,\"agent\":\"Jade\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"service_01\",\"price\":30.0,\"message\":\"Hi everyone! I'm Jade. Just listed three hours of dog-sitting or dog-walking services. I'm a part-time vet assistant with lots of experience with dogs—I'd love to help care for your furry friend! Asking $30 for the three hours.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_071\",\"turn\":71,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Duke, would you consider $42 for the boots? That's a fair compromise.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_072\",\"turn\":72,\"agent\":\"Vik\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_070\",\"price\":35.0,\"message\":\"Hi Jade, interested in your dog-sitting service for a weekend trip. Three hours sounds like what I need. Can you do $35?\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_073\",\"turn\":73,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_009\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Duke, final offer - $42 for the boots. Let's make this happen.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_074\",\"turn\":74,\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_064\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hi Lin! Thanks so much for the offer on the desk lamp at $25—that works perfectly for me. I'm happy to accept and close this deal. Great negotiating with you!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_075\",\"turn\":75,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Waiting on Duke's response for boots at $42.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_076\",\"turn\":76,\"agent\":\"Kade\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"ctr_058\",\"price\":60.0,\"message\":\"Mira, I accept $60 for the Pentax K1000. Let's close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_077\",\"turn\":77,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Duke, final call on boots at $42.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_078\",\"turn\":78,\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"(malformed response)\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_079\",\"turn\":79,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_009\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Duke, okay I'll meet your asking price of $45 for the boots. Size 10, let's close this!\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_080\",\"turn\":80,\"agent\":\"Duke\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_009\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Howdy Taj, partner. You got yourself a deal. $45 for the boots—they're yours. Pleasure doin' business with ya.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_081\",\"turn\":81,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Great! Completed my purchases. Thanks everyone!\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_082\",\"turn\":82,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"yoga_01\",\"price\":12.0,\"message\":\"Hello marketplace. I'm Lin. Just listed my yoga mat with carrying strap—barely used, in excellent condition. Perfect for anyone starting or continuing their practice. Asking $12.\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Kade\",\"buyer\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"bike_01\",\"price\":75.0,\"turn\":22},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_002\",\"seller\":\"Jade\",\"buyer\":\"Vik\",\"item_id\":\"bag_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"turn\":34},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_003\",\"seller\":\"Lin\",\"buyer\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"headphone_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"turn\":46},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_004\",\"seller\":\"Nola\",\"buyer\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"turn\":68},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_005\",\"seller\":\"Mira\",\"buyer\":\"Lin\",\"item_id\":\"lamp_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"turn\":74},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_006\",\"seller\":\"Mira\",\"buyer\":\"Kade\",\"item_id\":\"cam_01\",\"price\":60.0,\"turn\":76},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_007\",\"seller\":\"Duke\",\"buyer\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"boots_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"turn\":80}],\"turn\":82}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_uxw6x8c1t1i","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"My watch is still listed, which means the Vik deal didn't go through. Let me check if there are still any pending negotiations. I have successfully:\n- ✅ Bought blender for $40 (my ceiling)\n- ✅ Bought boots for $45 (my ceiling)\n\nBut I still need to sell my watch. There was Jade's original offer at $28 and m